{"tid":2498804,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"通訊事務管理局 : 有權檢查《理大圍城》放映會參加者身份證 !","createTime":"2021-04-21T11:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T13:33:53.000Z","uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0260ef0d7a30e7381e550d879a2593601d73f2d5","tid":2498804,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"【通訊事務管理局突發踩場 就職工盟《理大圍城》放映會作出疑似警告】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/175016756_5543857578987803_3060544966938896797_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=JU8a11v9AfMAX8_MNr2&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=0bc0a54cb3648586bfe2b67ca5d7a12f&amp;oe=60A7294E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.6435-9%2F175016756_5543857578987803_3060544966938896797_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DJU8a11v9AfMAX8_MNr2%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D0bc0a54cb3648586bfe2b67ca5d7a12f%26oe%3D60A7294E&h=53e138c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日下午約五時，電影、報刊及物品管理辦事處好大陣仗，派出六名職員，上嚟職工盟辦事處，要求我地交代嚟緊「理大圍城」嘅放映場次及負責人資料。<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱有權派人落嚟放映會現場，監察我地有無出示放映許可證及檢查參加者身份證。<br />\n<br />\n原來政府有呢個權力，以往唔見佢地有行使，《大公報》出完頭版同Ben周出言恐嚇，就嗱嗱聲要招呼我地，認真俾足面。<br />\n<br />\n由於事出突然，我地同合辦工會溝通後，佢地表示要多啲時間先了解有關部門嘅權力規定，所以今晚原訂放映會延期舉行。<br />\n<br />\n我地重申，坐定定戲照睇，唔會縮，同香港人一齊，風雨中抱緊自由。"},{"pid":"5f96481ba74d7e4e92a576927bf9fa5766e76e01","tid":2498804,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ffbd9403689345733cdf31aad502fedf2d36e0","tid":2498804,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:58:54.000Z","msg":"連登仔李伯盧開Patreon，需要大家支持！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2498797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2498797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e505e91e46a78079780535e1fccf40a6cf1e2af","tid":2498804,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5194c01f09610b889878d368a1c1d24b2f39e006","tid":2498804,"uid":97398,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"以後戲院洗唔洗實名買飛"},{"pid":"3097298b3e27bd8e3e06ba3fd5383e15685d7927","tid":2498804,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:11:54.000Z","msg":"播嘢都要你批准？"},{"pid":"ccba35ad1fce2b279c97e3c8f3fa40c52f5b8db8","tid":2498804,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"有權<br />\n依法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1beb868acaa8058c335eb3a32dd4b1bb0ef16bd2","tid":2498804,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"成班港共契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}